{"tid":101992,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好失敗......","createTime":"2017-01-31T09:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T19:07:14.000Z","uid":78620,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a998b2d004d3836332b4add7c35f3704d96ee8","tid":101992,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"我上年大學畢業,<br />\n原本番緊份合約工,<br />\n本應份合約去到十月先完,<br />\n上兩星期上司通知, <br />\n因為資金出現左D問題,<br />\n所以份合約去到三月就要停。<br />\n<br />\n感情生活空虛,<br />\n已經25歲仔拖都未拍過,<br />\n事關唔受香港人歡迎,<br />\n最hurt果次係同2個女同學傾計,<br />\n佢地話「如果俾我知道邊個係gay實唔同佢組group project, 最多只係同佢做朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n生涯規劃遙遙無期,<br />\n一直打算出國留學順手移民,<br />\n每個月洗費好少但都儲唔到幾多錢, 投資又失利,<br />\n好彩最近父母話可以借錢俾我留學, 算係少樣野煩,<br />\n只係我唔想依賴父母太多。<br />\n<br />\n最近因為存在感薄弱上黎連登開個account,<br />\n(好多年前高登有account, 不過俾人ban左就無再上去),<br />\n新年諗住玩下改圖刷下存在感,<br />\n點知玩左幾日改極都係無人理。<br />\n起初以為自己功力退步左, 幽默感差左,<br />\n今日發現有人轉貼我D圖有好多人覆, <br />\n先發現自己依家連存在感都刷唔到, <br />\n攪到我心都灰埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ......"},{"pid":"e6a9ff2a8661765e660da2a65ab67a97c0928c61","tid":101992,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"下面係依幾日改落嘅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7MmT89h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7MmT89h.jpg&h=2a9f3c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UUN3z3Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUUN3z3Z.jpg&h=77e181a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3cT8IOl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3cT8IOl.jpg&h=b79da615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DSRmp9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDSRmp9f.jpg&h=5f0d895c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgu